      <title>Shopify 股价下跌，因为 2025 年初的现金流预测令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/shopify-beats-estimates-says-revenue-to-grow-mid-20-in-first-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电子商务公司 Shopify Inc. 预计的自由现金流令投资者失望，掩盖了其假日购物季强劲的表现，随后股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/shopify-beats-estimates-says-revenue-to-grow-mid-20-in-first-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 12:16:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orcel 称 UniCredit 将在一年内决定德国商业银行的收购报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/unicredit-s-orcel-says-commerzbank-decision-about-a-year-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 首席执行官 Andrea Orcel 希望在今年年底决定是否对德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 发出收购要约，并将这一决定与下一届德国政府是否愿意让这笔交易实现挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/unicredit-s-orcel-says-commerzbank-decision-about-a-year-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 10:22:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟承诺对特朗普的金属关税采取反制措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/eu-says-it-will-impose-countermeasures-against-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟誓言将对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布的美国将对钢铁和铝进口征收 25% 的关税作出回应，此举将加剧美国与最亲密盟友之一之间的贸易争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/eu-says-it-will-impose-countermeasures-against-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税给动荡的铝市场带来新一轮动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-tariffs-spell-fresh-turmoil-for-volatile-aluminum-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易商争相评估特朗普总统领导下美国贸易保护主义再度抬头的潜在影响，全球铝市场正进入新的动荡时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/trump-tariffs-spell-fresh-turmoil-for-volatile-aluminum-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 04:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
